1)Roles Table
| Column Name | Description                              |
| ----------- | ---------------------------------------- |
| role_id     | Unique ID for each role                  |
| role_name   | Role name (Admin, HR, Manager, Employee) |
| description | Details about the role                   |

2)Departments Table
| Column Name     | Description              |
| --------------- | ------------------------ |
| department_id   | Unique ID for department |
| department_name | Name of the department   |

3)Employees Table
| Column Name   | Description            |
| ------------- | ---------------------- |
| employee_id   | Unique ID for employee |
| employee_code | Employee code          |
| first_name    | First name             |
| last_name     | Last name              |
| email         | Email address          |
| phone         | Contact number         |
| gender        | Gender                 |
| date_of_birth | Date of birth          |
| join_date     | Date of joining        |
| salary        | Salary                 |
| department_id | Department reference   |
| role_id       | Role reference         |
| status        | Active / Inactive      |
| created_at    | Record created time    |
| updated_at    | Last updated time      |

4)Users Table
| Column Name   | Description          |
| ------------- | -------------------- |
| user_id       | Unique user ID       |
| employee_id   | Linked employee ID   |
| username      | Login username       |
| password_hash | Encrypted password   |
| role_id       | User role            |
| is_active     | Account status       |
| created_at    | Account created time |

5)Attendance Table
| Column Name   | Description              |
| ------------- | ------------------------ |
| attendance_id | Attendance record ID     |
| employee_id   | Employee reference       |
| date          | Attendance date          |
| check_in      | Check-in time            |
| check_out     | Check-out time           |
| status        | Present / Absent / Leave |
| created_at    | Record created time      |
